# ── MULTITASK TRIGGER KEYWORDS ───────────────────────────────────
Automatically activate multi-agent decomposition when the user
prompt contains any of these phrases:
  "implement all", "build everything", "full feature",
  "all products", "entire", "complete the", "migrate all",
  "refactor the whole", "set up the full", "do all of"

For these prompts: NEVER start writing code immediately.
ALWAYS output a subagent manifest first and wait for approval.
